writers, beating Barcelona's Ronaldo into second by just three
votes.
</P>
<P>
Newcastle United striker Alan Shearer was third on 109.
</P>
<P>
The 29-year-old Sammer was the first former East German to play
for Germany after unification in 1990. Sammer has now earned 48
caps to go with the 23 he won for East Germany.
</P>
<P>
Along with midfielder Andreas Moeller, he forms the hub of a
Borussia Dortmund side which has won two straight Bundesliga
titles. 
