<HEADLINE> Ramos Meets Cabinet Members After Operation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, December 24 (Xinhua) -- Philippine President Fidel
Ramos, who underwent a carotid operation Sunday morning, today met
briefly with members of his cabinet and mediamen at the Makati
Medical Center here.
</P>
<P>
The Presidential Press Office said that during the meeting,
Ramos showed "none of the effects of his one-hour and 15-minute
operation" to clear a blockage in a carotid artery.
</P>
