economics, modern science and technology, and even foreign
languages, and computer skills," he added.
</P>
<P>
He pledged that starting next year, personnel departments at
all levels will improve their work efficiency and quality of
service, and play an active and significant role in local economic
growth and social progress.
</P>
<P>
"We will also work out and complete a whole set of service
standards, and increase the transparency of our work to receive
the supervision of the general public," he added. 
