<DATE_TIME> 1996-12-24 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> State Nonferrous Metals Industry Corp. Becomes Holding Company </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 24 (Xinhua) -- The China National Nonferrous
Metals Industry Corporation has won the approval from the State
Council, China's highest governing body, to begin pilot reforms
of the business and its affiliations.
